<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="standard-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" author="Kieran O'Donnell" dateTime="2021-03-29T09:20:44" id="_02c40f24-7c39-4ecd-bee5-3b1b2007160e" outputclass="standard-clause" type="insert"><sptc>6.2</sptc><title id="_4d276178-fe7d-4337-bf78-41d1d27cc47d">Construction</title><ol outputclass="numbered"><li id="_96da2ac8-e28c-432c-9e22-a5616970ece2">Reinforcing constructed in accordance with the requirements of (3) must be provided in the locations depicted in—<ol><li id="_ea0cbe16-1c38-40cf-85fe-934421c810ca"><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5040_0.19.0.xml#_33288ef9-8157-400c-9653-04accb2278cd" id="_74c36783-d922-452e-8e21-1e007673a784" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figures 6.2a</xref> or <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5041_0.11.0.xml#_c83f2c6d-dd5e-422c-973b-15be90e9b7c3" id="_b8b2c706-1b2a-401a-85dd-dea0365cfede" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">6.2b</xref> for walls surrounding a bath; and</li><li><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5042_0.18.0.xml#_be44e2aa-bd26-462b-9090-36df86abe4ba" id="_bdf22c59-a491-4cc0-bbe9-696c61866b9d" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figures 6.2c</xref> or <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5043_0.14.0.xml#_7e0d3eb4-2fad-4ad2-99b5-d08f148a71d7" id="_239d0811-6985-4b0c-b9e8-efbe9ee3426d" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">6.2d</xref> for shower walls; and</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5044_0.7.0.xml#_86ed24f5-c908-4887-afbd-5733c34155ef" id="_f688d977-4a88-4308-b4a2-a7bb3f360364" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 6.2e</xref> for a wall adjacent to and within 460 mm of the centreline of a toilet pan; and</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/6617_0.13.0.xml#_d109ef2f-307b-4f09-b967-75bb448dbdcf" id="_1bf9a940-714a-422d-8081-d0d7d933f7fe" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figures 6.2f</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/6620_0.9.0.xml#_84de4c6d-704b-479f-92da-81b7a8240f07" id="_b8c2f611-7b9c-49e2-ac0d-fa299e9d1d58" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">6.2g</xref> for a wall behind a toilet pan where a wall described in (c) is not provided or a window sill or a door encroaches on the area <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_142fc430-dabe-4391-9906-93a2f7839a4b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be provided with reinforcing or where the toilet pan is not provided in a corner of the bathroom.</li></ol></li><li id="_7b45e4b8-0eb9-4333-9e0f-0edbaa183e9b">Reinforcing need only be provided across the available width of the wall where a wall referred to in (1)(a) or (b)—<ol><li id="_ccc5a42b-de67-49f7-9a64-dbfd7216a0e5">is narrower than the width of the area <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_20cde941-2acf-4e14-99b1-526eb3cc3323" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be provided with reinforcing; or</li><li>terminates at a window sill lower than the height of the area nominated to be provided with reinforcing.</li></ol></li><li id="_9d6140e2-872d-4de9-b1aa-a6585be7ceb5">Reinforcing required by (1) must be constructed using one of the following materials:<ol><li id="_895472fb-f3e5-472d-918e-31fb3b4b9e44">A minimum of 12 mm thick structural grade plywood, or similar.</li><li>Timber framing with a minimum thickness of 25 mm.</li><li>Light gauge steel framing noggings or metal plate in accordance with the NASH Standard.</li></ol></li></ol><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5040_0.19.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-26T14:30:37" id="_33288ef9-8157-400c-9653-04accb2278cd" type="insert"><num/><title id="_44db3bf4-6056-40b1-a4bb-c01bda1865e2"/></image-reference><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5041_0.11.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-26T14:30:48" id="_c83f2c6d-dd5e-422c-973b-15be90e9b7c3" type="insert"><num/><title id="_b9675678-203c-4538-aaff-794c4335603e"/></image-reference><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5042_0.18.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-26T14:31:05" id="_be44e2aa-bd26-462b-9090-36df86abe4ba" type="insert"><num/><title id="_bed94972-f336-4e1f-a5bc-6d7aae57e1c5"/></image-reference><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5043_0.14.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-26T14:31:17" id="_7e0d3eb4-2fad-4ad2-99b5-d08f148a71d7" type="insert"><num/><title id="_ffd2507e-ea91-44af-a6bd-81af08290e0c"/></image-reference><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/5044_0.7.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-